pageContext.claim: “In fact, they have polls -- enthusiasm polls, they call them -- that have us at a level that we've never been at before. The Democrats always had the edge on that. We are higher than them. We have more enthusiasm.”
pageContext.analysis: This lacks context. The same poll that showed higher enthusiasm among Trump voters (by not much) showed that every Democratic candidate included in the survey would beat Trump by at least 6 points.
